DISCIPLINARY COUNSEL
v.
MOORE 2018-0402 Supreme Court of Ohio. July 26, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

DISCIPLINARY CASES

On respondent's motion for leave to file an answer. Motion granted. This matter is remanded to the Board of Professional Conduct for further proceedings under Gov.Bar R. V(12). The interim default suspension imposed against respondent on April 16, 2018, shall remain in place while this matter is pending before the board. DeGenaro, J., not participating.
